Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiting gets us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a step forward into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a deduction and love countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Astrology can't solve it itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's solve the case quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's essential for a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To capture objective leads in a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, by not allowing subjective feelings to get in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Systematic deductions can be carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:20.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Say, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the astrology that I practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:22.24,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,0} Shijou Reika (38)\NAstrologist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You don't believe in it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it's different from fortune-telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Solving a case also requires a sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of which often comes in a flash of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flash of light that can see through the intuitive truth of a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you ever looked into this line of fortune-telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I should say "some"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of a curious publisher...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The widely famous astrologist, Shijou Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:56.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And the famous detective Mouri Kogoro\Nwere brought together for a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.61,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,0}Katsuragi Kensuke (45)\N"Starry Sky Weekly" President
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's how we've ended up here at Shijou Reika's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,0} Tamura Machio (32)\NEditor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I have a natural ability for detection...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As many times, I have solved them while unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really know how to tell jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, Nakame{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} from Tohto TV is on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,0} Shiraishi Yuuka (26)\NReika's Apprentice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He said it's important that he speaks with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm working right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm about to take the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, no need for that—just be natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a really nice house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was originally a very wealthy person's\Nvilla, before Reika bought it for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I meant Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's stained glass, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a personal design by Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see ones like it all around the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Above it is her profile, as well as her astrological sign—Scorpio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you make coffee this strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even have a nice aroma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare another batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Aren't you actress, Midorikawa Kurara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:32.25,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,0}Midorikawa Kurara (28)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is this a customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the famous detective, Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're having a discussion to be included as a special in the magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To behold you with my own eyes is an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, can I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I already paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should you really be saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I released even a bit of information on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, there's nothing I can do but quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to escape me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must find a replacement immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, a replacement for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as it's someone with money and privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find someone along those lines, and you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that handsome guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I will tell your fortune next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait here for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have some wine with the others in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please come to my room around 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have you tell my fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, that's why I forced my father to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to know, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems it's really troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll read your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't quite have the time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are many people waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As consolation, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't accept something so precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll let you hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just return it on the day I read your fortune, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will do my best to find time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you promise you would let me take over that column?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I originally intended to do just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika strongly opposed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you can tell fortunes by some other means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that you aren't good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just a front...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the proof that she hates me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tres bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did sensei scold you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei is always taking out her anger on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is her niece as well as her apprentice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she treats her more like a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's just another aspect of fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that special matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way is the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door on the left, all the way at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the left, to the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of playing soccer with Genta and the others, I'm stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! A red-flanked blue tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It actually made it all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called for her several times but she didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could she be asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She isn't the type to make her guests wait for extended periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, will you accompany me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange. Something could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's look from the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika, what's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, we can break in through the window on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll climb up and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, open the door so I'll have some footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you get inside, go unlock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entrance and exit doors are both locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the window is covered with bars...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sealed room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder victim is a fortune-telling astrologer, Shijou Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has likely been dead between three and three and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That puts the crime at about 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the door was locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all broke the window to get in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where was the key then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in that pile there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any spare keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her apprentice, Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, may have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a bird's feather fell in here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from a red-flanked blue tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around 5:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw one fly to the roof up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the feather fell in from the broken window...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange that the feather is under the glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop rummaging through the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you have a spare key to Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, only she had a key to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, as the one closest to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be easy to make a copy of that key, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you not be against her, since she halted\Nyou from writing the astrology column?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With sensei dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You serve to inherit her legacy, as the closest relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used a spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've already heard back on duplicates of the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was their conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a special hollow-point key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the manufacturer can duplicate this key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Duplicates can only be requested with the original credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, the chance of anyone but the owner getting one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is near zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called the manufacturer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was told this is the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case has become much more complex...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and since the key was inside the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sealed room murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} opened the door at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't he have hidden the real key?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I saw it from beginning to end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he didn't do anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was the last time you saw Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When sensei left the living room for her office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where did you go afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I talked with Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for a few minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was in the kitchen the rest of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, I was also in the kitchen helping\Nwith dinner and can confirm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same as Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the living room with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was discussing business on the phone at reception...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after 5:00, I was here with Tamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Midorikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... Just like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, when I went to the bathroom around 5:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were coming down from the 2nd floor, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was... My fortune-telling appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could Kurara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} have killed sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say such foolish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it when I came here last month for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were coming out of her room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid bitch... I'll take care of you sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika was a dispicable woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would have such an inviting face at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by using fortune-telling as a front...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had me tell her my deepest secrets and betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used astrology to extort large sums of money from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to stand my ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she threatened to leak my private information to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Extortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why you went to Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to her room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm working right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you prove that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you expect me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I once thought she was such a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now this extortion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before, I went to Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} to have my fortune told...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she said she didn't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She gave me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And said it was a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It used to be on her room's key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before she went in for Dad's reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the, "I'm working right now, I'll call later"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have I heard that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The design here is the same as the one on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we'd like for everyone to go the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And answer just a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all that wine getting to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on just one moment, Inspector{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-dono{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could settle for just taking the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You mean you know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick in this case isn't a complicated one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After they killed Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit walked out of the room with the key and locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, went up on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cracked the stained glass by making a hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And dropped the key from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red-flanked blue tail that Conan saw around 5:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Went over the hole the culprit made.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why its feather was under the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In what shards of the stained glass, there aren't any red pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the middle of the scorpio's image on the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would the culprit go to so\Nmuch effort to create a sealed room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To ensure that Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} becomes the scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was likely convinced Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a spare of the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since there isn't one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This simple murder became a sealed room one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean Midorikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the culprit, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Kurara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went to the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had already been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I heard her voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The conversation between Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I was recorded, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a call in the middle of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please play that back for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it's important that he speaks with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm working right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, it's me, Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm working right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait until I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's the one with the recording, Tamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tape recorder can be concealed in a pocket by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer who took the life of Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, it was you who suggested Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would have a spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to ask: Why didn't you ask Yuuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwhen you couldn't get the door open?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:20:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because I was in a bit of a panic and hurrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to prevent the hole from being found...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had to break the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let me ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you broke the glass and jumped down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a number of keys lying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You picked up this room's key without any hesitation, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know that key went to the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the key holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that she always keeps a sapphire pendant on her key holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, before this incident, what was\Non the key holder was changed slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} removed it from the keyring and gave it to my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sapphire key holder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She removed it just before she went into her office.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you did not see or talk to Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the key with the sapphire pendant is the one in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other than Reika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only other would be the culprit who created the sealed room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman was worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She demanded I repay all of her investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that if I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would get insider trading information from the publishing house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And sell it to the weekly magazines!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to learn from the fortune-telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know where Shin'ichi is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how he's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than worrying about Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be best to start thinking of how we'll get Uncle home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a "dream vision," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"24 Hours in the Life of Mouri Kogoro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came into this sealed room first to hide some evidence\Nthat you weren't able to remove earlier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wrong, this isn't an ordinary murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an impossible crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.79,0:24:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soaked Jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.96,0:24:51.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The playboy, Officer Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.67,0:24:52.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's a jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.63,0:24:54.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: Secret Love is brought to light.
